text: 3.9-10 Mat 9.21, 14.36, Mak 4.1, 5.29, 6.56, Luk 5.1-3, 7.21 Ned Jisas binɨb kuŋay nep gek suŋ lek, anɨb ak binɨb mɨñak gak okok, chɨn ap nop dɨnun suŋ laŋ agɨl owlak. Apɨl, pak pag yokɨl Jisas yɨl owlak. Pen nop dɨnɨgon chɨnop suŋ lɨnɨgab agɨl, ap tɨbɨk dɨl apelak, bɨne okok kɨlop agak, Bot olap dɨlɨtep gɨnɨmɨb agak.
